[u_1 u_2 \cdots u_r]  (v - 1 + (1+u_1)(1+u_2)\cdots(1+u_r))^n \\ = \sum_{q=0}^n {n\choose q} (v-1)^{n-q}  [u_1 u_2 u_3 \cdots u_r](1+u_1)^q(1+u_2)^q(1+u_3)^q\cdots(1+u_r)^q \\ = \sum_{q=0}^n {n\choose q} (v-1)^{n-q}  q[u_2 u_3 \cdots u_r](1+u_2)^q(1+u_3)^q\cdots(1+u_r)^q \\ = \sum_{q=0}^n {n\choose q} (v-1)^{n-q}  q^2[u_3 \cdots u_r](1+u_3)^q\cdots(1+u_r)^q \\ = \sum_{q=0}^n {n\choose q} (v-1)^{n-q} q^r.
